If you want to do any shopping nearby you would not be able to because there are not any shops.In{Costock}there are no shops only a{bread van}on Mondays and a{butcher's van}on Tuesdays and Fridays.
In{Rempstone}there are no shops either only a{mobile shop}which sells sweets,canned foods and vegetables.This comes once a week on Thursdays.If you want to do any big shopping for articles such as clothes or shoes then you would have to go to{ {Nottingham,Loughborough or Leicester.}
There were{Post Offices}in{Costock}and {Rempstone}but they have now been closed down.The villagers now have to go to either{East Leake}or{Wymeswold} for postal facilities.
